{
  "stem": "27509.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Alexander the Great did it willingly, but that's why he was Alexander the Great.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But-- but otherwise, people want to have one front and not to have-- to be challenged from the back.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that was the nature of the agreement The-- the Ribbentrop-Molotov Agreement secured-- secured for Germany a one-front situation.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The pack was signed in early '39.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And once that was signed, everybody knew war is coming.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was the 1st of September.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were home.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And at 9 o'clock, suddenly we had aeroplanes all over the city.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they came from a westerly direction at an angle going towards the railways-- railway yards.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we came down, of course.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We went out of the-- into the yard, and we heard explosions.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We knew that war has started.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that first feeling of looking up and seeing-- seeing bombs falling out from the aeroplanes and-- and saying which one is mine is the first encounter.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That was-- that was because the war started officially at 4 o'clock in the morning when they-- they crossed the border.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And whilst it took them three weeks to-- to-- to occupy Poland, the aeroplanes had no limits, of course, and they were everywhere at the same time.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So by the-- by the-- the first-- the first purpose of any military action is to disrupt communication of the enemy.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "If you disrupt the-- the-- the-- the railway lines and you can't send supplies, so you can't send reinforcements, and you can't send-- you have-- you have-- you have partly achieved your-- your-- your military purpose.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that was-- But I have a weak area.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I came from-- from the countryside on another of those missions of collecting-- of collecting [INAUDIBLE] and so on.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
